çš„ä¸€ä¸\ª<code>google.com</code>å°±ä¸èƒ½è§£æåˆ°è¿™äº›æœåŠ¡å™¨ä¸Šï¼Œè€Œä¸”ç”¨å¤šä¸ªäºŒçº§åŸŸåæ¯”å¦\‚<code>server1.google.com</code>ï¼\Œ<code>server2.google.com</code>ç­‰ç­‰ä¹Ÿç»™ç”¨æˆ·é€ æˆäº†ä½¿ç”¨ä¸Šçš„ä¸ä¾¿ï¼ˆä¸€ä¸‡å°æœåŠ¡å™¨ï¼Œä½ å’‹ä¸ä¸Šå¤©å‘¢?ï¼‰ï¼Œé‚£è¯¥æ€ä¹ˆåŠå‘¢ï¼Ÿé€šè¿‡åå‘ä»£ç†å¯ä»¥å¾ˆå¥½çš„è§£å†³è¿™ä¸ªé—®é¢˜ã€‚ä¸ºæ­¤ï¼Œæˆ‘ç»˜åˆ¶äº†ä¸‹é¢çš„ç¤ºæ„å›¾ï¼\š</p>\r\n<pre><code>                                                                   +-------------------+\r\n                                                                   |                   |\r\n                                                            +------&gt;   server 1        |\r\n+-------------+                                             |      |                   |\r\n|             +----------+                                  |      |                   |\r\n|  client 1   |          |                                  |      +-------------------+\r\n|             |          |                                  |\r\n+-------------+          |                                  |\r\n                         |         +------------------+     |      +-------------------+\r\n                         |         |                  |     |      |                   |\r\n+-------------+          |         |                  |     |      |   server 2        |\r\n|             |          |         |                  +------------&gt;                   |\r\n|  clent 2    +--------------------&gt;  reverse proxy   |     |      |                   |\r\n|             |          |         |                  |     |      +-------------------+\r\n+-------------+          |         |                  |     |\r\n                         |         |                  |     |               .\r\n      .                  |         |                  |     |               .\r\n      .                  |         +------------------+     |               .\r\n      .                  |                                  |\r\n                         |                                  |      +--------------------+\r\n+-------------+          |                                  |      |                    |\r\n|             |          |                                  |      |   server m         |\r\n|  client n   +----------+                                  +------&gt;                    |\r\n|             |                                                    |                    |\r\n+-------------+                                                    +--------------------+\r\n</code></pre><p>è€Œæœ¬æ–‡çš„ä¸»è§’ â€”â€\” Nginxå°±æ˜¯å¹²è¿™ä¸ªäº‹çš„ã€\‚</p>\r\n<h4 id=\"h4-2-\"><a name=\"2. é…ç½®åå‘ä»£ç†\" class=\"reference-link\"></a><span class=\"header-link octicon octicon-link\"></span>2. é…ç½®åå‘ä»£ç†</h4><h5 id=\"h5-2-1-node-server-\"><a name=\"2.1 åˆ©ç”¨ nodeå¯åŠ¨ä¸€ä¸ªæœ¬åœ°serverã€\‚\" class=\"reference-link\"></a><span class=\"header-link octicon octicon-link\"></span>2.1 åˆ©ç”¨ nodeå¯åŠ¨ä¸€ä¸ªæœ¬åœ°serverã€\‚</h5><pre><code class=\"lang-bash\">node index\r\n</code></pre>\r\n<p>å…¶ä¸­index.js</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"http://ondh71tpt.bkt.clouddn.com/img/posts/nginx/01.png\" alt=\"\">\r\n<h5 id=\"h5-2-2-hosts-\"><a name=\"2.2 é…ç½®hostsæ–‡ä»¶\" class=\"reference-link\"></a><span class=\"header-link octicon octicon-link\"></span>2.2 é…ç½®hostsæ–‡ä»¶</h5><p>ä»\¥<code>Linux</code>ä¸ºä¾‹ï¼\š</p>\r\n<pre><code class=\"lang-bash\">sudo vim /etc/hosts\r\n</code></pre>\r\n<p>ç„¶ååœ¨é‡Œé¢æ·»åŠ ä¸€æ¡è®°å½•ï¼š</p>\r\n<pre><code class=\"lang-bash\">test.com  127.0.0.1\r\n</code></pre>\r\n<h5 id=\"h5-2-3-nginx-conf\"><a name=\"2.3 é…ç½®nginx.conf\" class=\"reference-link\"></a><span class=\"header-link octicon octicon-link\"></span>2.3 é…ç½®nginx.conf</h5><p>åœ\¨<code>http</code>é‡Œé¢æ·»åŠ ï¼\š</p>\r\n<pre><code class=\"lang-bash\">#æœ¬åœ°http-serverå¼€å¯çš„serverï¼Œå‘½åä¸ºnode-serverï¼Œç›‘å\¬3000ç«¯å£\r\nupstream node-server{\r\n    server 127.0.0.1:3000;\r\n}\r\n\r\n# NGINX è™šæ‹Ÿä¸»æœºï¼Œç›‘å\¬8880ç«¯å£\r\nserver {\r\n    listen 8880;\r\n    server_name test.com;\r\n    access_log /var/log/nginx/node-server;\r\n\r\n    # Gzip Compression\r\n    gzip on;\r\n    gzip_comp_level 6;\r\n    gzip_vary on;\r\n    gzip_min_length  1000;\r\n    gzip_proxied any;\r\n    gzip_types text/plain text/css application/json application/x-javascript text/xml application/xml application/xml+rss text/javascript;\r\n    gzip_buffers 16 8k;\r\n\r\n    # åå‘ä»£ç† node-server\r\n    location / {\r\n      proxy_set_header X-Real-IP $remote_addr;\r\n      proxy_set_header X-Forwarded-For $proxy_add_x_forwarded_for;\r\n      proxy_set_header Host $http_host;\r\n      proxy_set_header X-NginX-Proxy true;\r\n      # ä»£ç†çš„åœ°å€\r\n      proxy_pass http://node-server;\r\n      proxy_redirect off;\r\n    }\r\n }\r\n</code></pre>\r\n<p>å¦‚æœéœ€è¦è½¬å‘æ‰€æœ‰çš„è¯·æ±‚ï¼Œä½¿ç”¨æ­£åˆ™è¡¨è¾¾å¼ï¼Œä½¿ç”\¨<code>~</code>å¯ç”¨æ­£åˆ™</p>\r\n<pre><code class=\"lang-bash\">  location ~ .*|/ {\r\n    proxy_pass 127.0.0.1:3000;\r\n  }\r\n</code></pre>\r\n<h4 id=\"h4-3-nginx\"><a name=\"3. å¯åŠ¨ Nginx\" class=\"reference-link\"></a><span class=\"header-link octicon octicon-link\"></span>3. å¯åŠ¨ Nginx</h4><pre><code class=\"lang-bash\">sudo service nginx start\r\n</code></pre>\r\n<h4 id=\"h4-4-\"><a name=\"4. æµ‹è¯•\" class=\"reference-link\"></a><span class=\"header-link octicon octicon-link\"></span>4. æµ‹è¯•</h4><p><img src=\"http://ondh71tpt.bkt.clouddn.com/img/posts/nginx/02.png\" alt=\"\"><br>å¯ä»¥çœ‹åˆ°ï¼Œå¯¹äºç”¨æˆ·çš„è¯·æ±‚ï¼Œæˆ‘ä»¬æˆåŠŸåå‘ä»£ç†åˆ°<code>127.0.0.1:3000</code>ä¸Šï¼</p>\r\n<h3 id=\"h3--\"><a name=\"å››ã€è´Ÿè½½å‡è¡\¡\" class=\"reference-link\"></a><span class=\"header-link octicon octicon-link\"></span>å››ã€è´Ÿè½½å‡è¡\¡</h3><p><code>è´Ÿè½½å‡è¡¡</code>ï¼Œè¿™ä¸ªåç§°å¬èµ·æ¥åˆåˆçš„æœ‰æœ¨æœ‰ï¼å…¶å®å˜›ï¼Œä¹Ÿå°±é‚£å›äº‹ï¼Œä¸è¦è¢«è¿™ç‰›é€¼å“„å“„çš„åè¯å“ä½äº†ã€‚ä¹‹å‰æˆ‘ä»¬åˆ†æäº†<code>google.com</code>æ˜¯æ€ä¹ˆå¯¹è¯·æ±‚è¿›è¡Œåˆ†æµçš„ï¼Œç°åœ¨æˆ‘ä»¬å°±æ¥å°å°çš„è¯•éªŒä¸€ä¸‹ã€\‚</p>\r\n<h4 id=\"h4-1-server\"><a name=\"1. å¦å¼€å¯ä¸€ä¸ªæœ¬åœ°server\" class=\"reference-link\"></a><span class=\"header-link octicon octicon-link\"></span>1. å¦å¼€å¯ä¸€ä¸ªæœ¬åœ°server</h4><pre><code class=\"lang-bash\">http-server -p 3001\r\n</code></pre>\r\n<p>åœ¨æ­¤serverçš„æ ¹ç›®å½•ä¸‹æ–°å»\º<code>index.html</code>ï¼Œè¾“å…¥â€™hello, nginx (server 2)â€\™</p>\r\n<h4 id=\"h4-2-nginx-conf\"><a name=\"2. é…ç½®nginx.conf\" class=\"reference-link\"></a><span class=\"header-link octicon octicon-link\"></span>2. é…ç½®nginx.conf</h4><p>ä¿®æ”¹ä¹‹å‰çš„é…ç½®ä¸ºï¼\š</p>\r\n<pre><code class=\"lang-bash\">#æœ¬åœ°http-serverå¼€å¯çš„serverï¼Œå‘½åä¸ºnode-serverï¼Œç›‘å\¬3000å’\Œ3001ç«¯å£\r\nupstream node-server{\r\n# weightè¡¨ç¤ºæƒé‡ï¼Œæ•°å€¼è¶Šå¤§ï¼Œè¡¨ç¤ºè¢«åˆ†é…åˆ°è¿™ä¸ªserverçš„å‡ ç‡è¶Šå¤§ï¼Œè¿™é‡Œæˆ‘ä»¬è®©å…¶ç›¸ç­‰ã€\‚\r\n    server 127.0.0.1:3000 weight=1;\r\n    server 127.0.0.1:3001 weight=1;\r\n}\r\n\r\n# NGINX è™šæ‹Ÿä¸»æœºï¼Œç›‘å\¬80ç«¯å£\r\nserver {\r\n    listen 80;\r\n    server_name test.com;\r\n    access_log /var/log/nginx/node-server;\r\n\r\n    # Gzip Compression\r\n    gzip on;\r\n    gzip_comp_level 6;\r\n    gzip_vary on;\r\n    gzip_min_length  1000;\r\n    gzip_proxied any;\r\n    gzip_types text/plain text/css application/json application/x-javascript text/xml application/xml application/xml+rss text/javascript;\r\n    gzip_buffers 16 8k;\r\n\r\n    # åå‘ä»£ç† node-server\r\n    location / {\r\n      proxy_set_header X-Real-IP $remote_addr;\r\n      proxy_set_header X-Forwarded-For $proxy_add_x_forwarded_for;\r\n      proxy_set_header Host $http_host;\r\n      proxy_set_header X-NginX-Proxy true;\r\n      # ä»£ç†çš„åœ°å€\r\n      proxy_pass http://node-server;\r\n      proxy_redirect off;\r\n    }\r\n }\r\n</code></pre>\r\n<h4 id=\"h4-3-nginx\"><a name=\"3. é‡å¯Nginx\" class=\"reference-link\"></a><span class=\"header-link octicon octicon-link\"></span>3. é‡å¯Nginx</h4><pre><code class=\"lang-bash\">sudo nginx -s reload\r\n</code></pre>\r\n<p>æˆ–è€\…</p>\r\n<pre><code class=\"lang-bash\">sudo service nginx restart\r\n</code></pre>\r\n<h4 id=\"h4-4-\"><a name=\"4. æµ‹è¯•\" class=\"reference-link\"></a><span class=\"header-link octicon octicon-link\"></span>4. æµ‹è¯•</h4><p><img src=\"http://ondh71tpt.bkt.clouddn.com/img/posts/nginx/03.png\" alt=\"\">\r\n<p><img src=\"http://ondh71tpt.bkt.clouddn.com/img/posts/nginx/04.png\" alt=\"\">\r\n<p>æˆ‘ä»¬å¯ä»¥çœ‹åˆ°ï¼Œå¯¹äºåŒä¸€ä¸ªè¯·æ±‚ï¼Œnginxä¼šæŒ‰ç…§æƒé‡éšæœºçš„åˆ†é…åˆ°ä¸åŒçš„serverï¼è¿™æ ·å°±å®Œæˆäº†å‡è¡¡è´Ÿè½½ã€‚å¯¹äºclientæ¥è¯´ï¼Œå¥½åƒå°±åªæœ‰ä¸€å°serverï¼\</p>\r\n<h3 id=\"h3--\"><a name=\"äº”ã€é—®é¢˜è§£å†\³\" class=\"reference-link\"></a><span class=\"header-link octicon octicon-link\"></span>äº”ã€é—®é¢˜è§£å†\³</h3><p><strong>è§£å†³Nginxçš„connect() to 127.0.0.1:8080 failed (13: Permission denied) while connect</strong></p>\r\n<p>åœ¨è¿›è¡ŒNginx+Tomcat è´Ÿè½½å‡è¡¡çš„æ—¶å€™é‡åˆ°äº†è¿™ä¸ªæƒé™é—®é¢˜ï¼Œåœ¨error.logæ—¥å¿—ä¸­ï¼Œæˆ‘ä»¬å¯ä»¥çœ‹åˆ°å¦‚ä¸‹ï¼\š</p>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n<p>connect() to 127.0.0.1:8080 failed (13: Permission denied) while connecting to upstream,</p>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<p>ç»è¿‡ä¸€ç•ªæ£€æŸ¥ä»¥åŠgoogle,åº”è¯¥æ˜¯SeLinuxçš„å¯¼è‡´çš„ã€‚å¯ä»¥é€‰æ‹©ä¸€äº›ä¸¤ç§æ–¹å¼è¿›è¡Œï¼š</p>\r\n<p>ç»è¿‡ä¸€ç•ªæ£€æŸ¥ä»¥åŠgoogle,åº”è¯¥æ˜¯SeLinuxçš„å¯¼è‡´çš„ã€‚å¯ä»¥é€‰æ‹©ä¸€äº›ä¸¤ç§æ–¹å¼è¿›è¡Œï¼š<br>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n<p><a href=\"http://www.hpboys.com/824.html\">CentOSä¸‹æŸ¥çœ‹SeLinuxçŠ¶æ€åŠå…³é—­SeLinux</a></p>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<p>2ã€æ‰§è¡Œä¸‹é¢çš„å‘½ä»¤</p>\r\n<pre><code class=\"lang-bash\">setsebool -P httpd_can_network_connect 1\r\n</code></pre>\r\n<h3 id=\"h3--centos-selinux-selinux\"><a name=\"å…­ã€CentOSä¸‹æŸ¥çœ‹SeLinuxçŠ¶æ€åŠå…³é—­SeLinux\" class=\"reference-link\"></a><span class=\"header-link octicon octicon-link\"></span>å…­ã€CentOSä¸‹æŸ¥çœ‹SeLinuxçŠ¶æ€åŠå…³é—­SeLinux</h3><h4 id=\"h4-1-selinux-\"><a name=\"1.æŸ¥çœ‹SELinuxçŠ¶æ€ï¼š\" class=\"reference-link\"></a><span class=\"header-link octicon octicon-link\"></span>1.æŸ¥çœ‹SELinuxçŠ¶æ€ï¼š</h4><pre><code class=\"lang-bash\">/usr/sbin/sestatus -v      #å¦‚æœSELinux statuså‚æ•°ä¸ºenabledå³ä¸ºå¼€å¯çŠ¶æ€\\r\n</code></pre>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n<p>SELinux status:                 enabled</p>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<pre><code class=\"lang-bash\">getenforce                 #ä¹Ÿå¯ä»¥ç”¨è¿™ä¸ªå‘½ä»¤æ£€æŸ\¥\r\n</code></pre>\r\n<h4 id=\"h4-2-selinux-\"><a name=\"2.å…³é—­SELinuxï¼\š\" class=\"reference-link\"></a><span class=\"header-link octicon octicon-link\"></span>2.å…³é—­SELinuxï¼\š</h4><p>1ã€ä¸´æ—¶å…³é—­ï¼ˆä¸ç”¨é‡å¯æœºå™¨ï¼‰ï¼š</p>\r\n<pre><code class=\"lang-bash\">setenforce 0                  #è®¾ç½®SELinux æˆä¸ºpermissiveæ¨¡å¼\r\n#setenforce 1                   #è®¾ç½®SELinux æˆä¸ºenforcingæ¨¡å¼\r\n</code></pre>\r\n<p>2ã€ä¿®æ”¹é…ç½®æ–‡ä»¶ï¼ˆéœ€è¦é‡å¯æœºå™¨ï¼‰ï¼\š</p>\r\n<p>ä¿®æ”¹<code>/etc/selinux/config</code> æ–‡ä»¶</p>\r\n<p>å°\†<code>SELINUX=enforcing</code>æ”¹ä¸º<code>SELINUX=disabled</code></p>\r\n<p>é‡å¯æœºå™¨å³å¯</p>\r\n<hr>\r\n<p><strong>å‚è€ƒèµ„æ–\™</strong></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"http://natumsol.github.io/2016/03/16/nginx-basic/\">http://natumsol.github.io/2016/03/16/nginx-basic/</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"http://www.hpboys.com/827.html\">http://www.hpboys.com/827.html</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"http://www.hpboys.com/824.html\">http://www.hpboys.com/824.html</a></p>','','','1','37','blog','4','0','0','n','n','n','y','y','','','1','0,0');
